beer.beer_description: Holland Import is a global premium beer. With its golden color and delicate smell of hops and malt. Holland Import is the quintessential pilsner beer. Holland Import is medium-bodied, dry and well-proportioned with a characteristic hop bitterness that supports its fine structure. Holland Import is the perfect accompaniment for a meal with friends and family, or any occasion when good friends meet. In the weekends or on a weekday evening. Celebrate the happy things in your life with a Holland Import!
